data.description: Practical & spacious 4-bedroom, 3-full bathroom is a testament to comfortable living. Boasting a 2-car garage, this home offers both convenience & style. Bright & open living space w/ high vaulted ceilings bathes the room in natural light. Kitchen features quartz countertops & stainless steel appliances. Designed for versatility, w/ a convenient bedroom & full bathroom on the1st floor, perfect for guests or a home office. Upstairs, you'll find cozy carpeted bedrooms, providing a warm & inviting atmosphere, while the living areas feature wood laminate plank vinyl flooring, easy to maintain. A/C system replaced in 2021, Solar panels were installed in 2020, significantly reducing your energy bills and helping the environment. The Desert Creek neighborhood offers an unbeatable location. A short drive away from the famous Las Vegas Strip, major highways, & excellent shopping opportunities. The community also has a separate RV parking area, a pool, & a park.
